     C* Phase 5 end-to-end: cycle + COMP + GOTO selective sum.
     C* Read records, sum only values strictly greater than 4.
     C* Data 003/005/002/008/001 -> 5+8 = 13 -> exit 13.
     FTRANS   IP  F    80              DISK
     ITRANS   AA  01
     I                                        1   30AMT
     C           AMT       COMP 4                    20
     C  N20                GOTO SKIP
     C                     ADD  AMT       RPGRET
     C           SKIP      TAG
